underlying_goal: To trace the source and fix the description of the 'Lab Safety' requirements in the technical report, which were poorly documented.
primary_success: Successfully traced the undocumented source of a set of requirements by investigating the project's Streamlit application code, resolving a discrepancy between the report's claims and the actual implementation.
brief_summary: The user questioned the origin of 'Lab Safety' requirements mentioned in their report. Claude investigated the codebase, found a discrepancy in name and count (15 'Commitments' vs 18 'Standards'), and discovered the true source (Anthropic/OpenAI RSPs) documented in the Streamlit UI code. The session concluded after confirming the report had already been corrected in a previous session.
